\c 2 Rute anosangana naBhoazi 1 Zvino Naomi wakanga ane hama yomurume wake, murume wakanga ane simba nepfuma, weimba yaErimereki, wainzi Bhoazi. 2 Rute muMoabhu akati kuna Naomi, "Nditenderei ndiende kumunda, ndindounganidza hura dzezviyo shure kwaiye unondinzwira nyasha." Akati kwaari, "Enda hako, mwana wangu." 3 Iye akaenda, akandounganidza pamunda achitevera vacheki; akava neropa rakanaka kuti wakasvika pamunda waBhoazi weimba yaErimereki.
